Morningstarin analyysi

This ETF provides exposure to German large-capitalisation equities, and can be used as a core holding for investors looking to build a German-centric portfolio. The fund can also act as a tactical tool to overweight German equities within a...

Sijoituspolitiikka: db x-trackers DAX® UCITS ETF (DR) 1C (EUR) | DBXD
The investment seeks to replicate, net of expenses, the DAX®Index. The fund will invest in the securities that consitutent the underlying index.
